Maintainer: Nicolas Frerebeau <nicolas.frerebeau@u-bordeaux-montaigne.fr>
Description: A toolkit for archaeological time series analysis. This package 
    provides a system of classes and methods to represent and work with 
    archaeological time series. Dates are represented as "rata die" and can be
    converted to (virtualy) any calendar defined by Reingold and Dershowitz 
    (2018) <doi:10.1017/9781107415058>.
